  <subtitle id="0">
    <StartTime>3</StartTime>
    <Text>Katie... I'm so sorry.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="1">
    <StartTime>6</StartTime>
    <Text>That I can't be there to see you in person.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="2">
    <StartTime>9.25</StartTime>
    <Text>That I can't tell you all this myself.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="3">
    <StartTime>12</StartTime>
    <Text>But I hope, as you read this journal, and you think back, that you'll understand why I had to do what I did.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="4">
    <StartTime>20.25</StartTime>
    <Text>And that you won't be sad and you won't hate me and you'll just know...</Text>
  </subtitle>  
  <subtitle id="5">
    <StartTime>26</StartTime>
    <Text>that I am where I need to be.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="6">
    <StartTime>29.5</StartTime>
    <Text>I love you so much, Katie. I'll see you again.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="7">
    <StartTime>34</StartTime>
    <Text>Someday.</Text>
  </subtitle>
  <subtitle id="7">
    <StartTime>36.5</StartTime>
    <Text>Love, Sam.</Text>
  </subtitle>
